      "_comment": "Segments where at least one page has significant tabular data structures. min_draw_count was previously ignored by the code (hardcoded to 150) -- as of the pss_classifier.py fix this value is now actually read. Set to 200 (higher than the old hardcoded 150) to directly address the known 'contains_tables still firing incorrectly on some segments' issue -- text-heavy FMS forms with vector borders/boxes were crossing 150 without being true tables.",
